org.apache.hive.hcatalog.data.transfer

Interface WriterContext

  • All Superinterfaces:
    Externalizable, Serializable

    public interface WriterContext
extends Externalizable
    This contains information obtained at master node to be distributed to slaves nodes that will do the writing. This class implements Externalizable so it can be serialized using standard Java mechanisms. Master should serialize it and make it available to slaves to prepare for writes.

    • Method Summary

      • Methods inherited from interface java.io.Externalizable

        readExternal, writeExternal
